Good class, good professor but tends to change topics a little to frequently.  Helps out by giving handouts, practice problems (with solutions), and past exams (with solutions).  Quite similar to FIN541.

Never met a soul who doesn't like Prof. Cannaday. Great guy; gives loads of handouts in the form of lecture notes, exam-prep sheets, or review topics. Midterm, 2 appraisals and final. Most people get an A on the midterm and do well on the appraisals. The final is no harder than the midterm, but students mess it up somehow and get like a B+.
